text.tspan: Share of industry in employment vs. GDP per capita, 1800 to 2015

GDP per capita, adjusted for inflation and for differences in living costs between countries.
Data source: Our World In Data based on Herrendorf et al. (2014) and GGDC-10 (2015); Bolt and van Zanden - Maddison Project Database
